 However, anytime I have grouped with another Enchanter and the Mez cycle starts to get broke down and I react quickly and decisivally to that situation with a sortie of AoE's, the blame for the broken cycle is <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  always</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> leveled on me, the Wizard. I then spend the next 20 min or so telling the Enchanter to watch and see who broke the Mez cycle to begin with.<br>
